{"tid":402330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(統計分享) 絲打請入 去女廁洗唔洗預時間","createTime":"2017-09-16T10:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T13:56:37.000Z","uid":137768,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9d50d3b0413e30211adee1490e44db263ec61e41","tid":402330,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"差唔多次次喺出面去廁所都會見到女廁排晒大隊<br />\n其實洗唔洗預早去到排隊廢事太急忍得太辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋會唔會發生啲咩尷尬事 <br />\n例如有人太急叫你俾佢排先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n統計一下:<br />\n<br />\n梗係要預早去定排隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊洗預早 好忍得 急先去都未遲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac7a01c3a19123813bdfc95dca6ef8a2017ab37","tid":402330,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab04a2293d0da53fab5ebf3201dd8f99e84562bd","tid":402330,"uid":39971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:43:41.000Z","msg":"要預飲水時間"},{"pid":"7cefcfcd626f91ae4e68a9798fcd9e77d2ca2f66","tid":402330,"uid":83173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:45:09.000Z","msg":"唔會，但見到條隊咁長惟有忍唔排 ，有時排完廁所又污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a78baa464c3d578c55f3335c090b796e2ae0f9","tid":402330,"uid":140113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T11:57:33.000Z","msg":"試過排到我去個陣<br />\n有個呀嬸帶住個呀婆話<br />\n可唔可以比呀婆去先<br />\n佢好似問咗等於我一定比<br />\n直接衝入厠所<br />\n屌你<br />\n我都好急尿呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c6f21536cb18f79993f3d7449f230ce767dfd9","tid":402330,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13